      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation outputs must be compared against experimental measurements using a quantitative metric with uncertainty bounds at Level 3.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index predictions compared against experimental measurements using normalised RMSE and Bland-Altman analysis. Predictions fall within experimental uncertainty bands at 4 of 5 operating points. Level 3 comparison criteria satisfied."
