      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoIs used in validation must directly correspond to the clinical hemolysis index required for regulatory decision at Level 4.",
      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) expressed in mg/dL, directly corresponding to the regulatory acceptance threshold. QoI relevance is fully established."
    },
    {
