      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence of the solver must be demonstrated with residuals below 1e-5 and monitored QoI stabilisation at Level 3.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged to residuals below 1e-6 with hemolysis index QoI stable to within 0.1% over the final 500 iterations. Solver error is well controlled."
