      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation setup must be reviewed by an independent analyst and documented in a simulation plan to control user-introduced error at Level 3.",
      "rationale": "Simulation plan reviewed by a second analyst prior to execution. Boundary condition inputs cross-checked against experimental test report. No use errors identified during independent review."
