      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed over blood viscosity, hematocrit, and hemolysis model coefficients. Input distributions derived from published physiological ranges. 10,000-sample Monte Carlo analysis completed; 95th percentile hemolysis index reported."
